                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Leverage experienced employees for mentoring and knowledge transfer programs for junior staff.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Introduce performance-linked incentives to further improve productivity and retention.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Develop center-of-excellence teams in high-growth areas like Cloud and Data &amp; AI.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Focus should be on converting Average (325) employees into high performers through targeted training programs.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Performance score distribution is positively skewed towards higher scores (3–5 levels account for majority employees)</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>, </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>showing</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>Æ </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>a generally healthy performance           culture. However, low-score</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10' italic='true'>Æ </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>employees (1–2) should be identified for performance improvement plans.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Proactive engagement programs should be introduced for medium and high-risk employees</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Promotion cycles should be optimized to improve employee satisfaction and retention.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Project execution monitoring should be strengthened to ensure timely completion.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Delayed and on-hold projects should be reviewed to identify root causes such as resource or dependency issues.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Red projects require immediate escalation, while Amber projects should be proactively monitored to prevent further deterioration.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Diversification into high-growth sectors like E-commerce and Healthcare can improve portfolio balance.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Time sheet accuracy and automation should be enhanced to improve reporting efficiency.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Total overtime hours are 13.98K, which is significant compared to total working hours.This indicates potential workload concentration and requires better capacity planning to avoid employee burnout.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Current attendance policies appear effective and well-structured</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Workforce planning is well balanced with no major seasonal disruption.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ea1c1c' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>: Overtime trend is also consistent (~1.1K–1.2K monthly), indicating that overtime demand is steady rather than irregular spikes.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
